OL,5,G0000 Skin A&E
OL,6,     FDr Adil Sheraz removes a giant
OL,7,     Flipoma from a patient's back,
OL,8,     Fwhile Dr Toby Nelson tackles 13
OL,9,     Flipomas on a single patient, and
OL,10,     Fthere's a nasty face cyst for Dr
OL,11,     FEmma McMullen.
OL,12,G0100 Nightmare Tenants, Slum Landlords
OL,13,     FBen from Lewisham Council's Rogue
OL,14,     FLandlord Unit has just 24 hours to
OL,15,     Frehouse a single mother and her
OL,16,     Fchild or they will end up on the
OL,17,     Fstreets.
OL,18,G0200 Nightmare Tenants, Slum Landlords
OL,19,     FMargaret tries to get the #20,000
OL,20,     Fshe is owed from a letting agent,
OL,21,     FStavros and Emily try to get their
OL,22,     Fhouse back from squatters.
